{"url": "https://www.harpersbazaar.com/celebrity/latest/a20645416/miranda-kerr-gives-birth-first-child-evan-spiegel/", "text": "2 min read\n\nMiranda Kerr is now a mom of four.\n\nThe veteran Victoria\u2019s Secret model announced today on Instagram that she has welcomed her fourth son, baby Pierre.\n\nKerr is also mom to boys Hart, five, and Myles, four, with husband Evan Spiegel, CEO of Snap Inc. She also shares son Flynn, 12, with ex-husband Orlando Bloom.\n\n(Kerr and Bloom divorced in 2013, and the model married Spiegel in 2017. Bloom is now engaged to Katy Perry, and the two welcomed their first child, Daisy Dove Bloom, in August 2020.)\n\nJeff Kravitz // Getty Images\n\nIn her Instagram announcement, Kerr shared a photo of a bouquet of yellow flowers on a table next to a light blue blanket embroidered with the name Pierre, plus a pair of teeny-tiny yellow Louis Vuitton monogram socks.\n\n\u201cWe are overjoyed by the arrival of our little ray of sunshine, Pierre Kerr Spiegel. We couldn\u2019t be more excited to welcome our fourth son into our family. Feeling so very blessed \ud83d\ude4f\ud83d\udc7c\ud83c\udf08\ud83c\udf3b,\u201d she captioned the post.\n\nKerr announced on Snapchat in September that she was pregnant with her fourth child. She revealed her baby bump in a Reformation x Christy Dawn crop top and jeans.\n\n\u201cSo excited to announce baby no. 4,\u201d she wrote over the first shot. She added in another: \u201cAnd it\u2019s a boy.\u201d\n\nIn July 2022, before welcoming Pierre, Kerr revealed in an interview that she had always wanted to be a boy mom. \u201cI just love being a mother and I always wanted three boys,\u201d she said, \u201cso I feel really blessed that I have three healthy boys.\u201d", "images": ["https://www.harpersbazaar.com/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/social/youtube.ce3e1ae.svg?primary=%2523000000&id=social-button-icon", "https://www.harpersbazaar.com/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/search.f1c199c.svg", "https:/